We build and embrace\nshared technology.
We also create open source\nconstruction machines,
which we argue inevitably\naffect how we think
and design through making.
In our work, we aim to mind the\ntension between machine means
and architectural\nends across scales.
And we reclaim authorship\nover processes of construction
that influence the way\nwe can build or perhaps
ought to build in the future.
At various scales,\nour work's performance
and architectural\nexpression are inherently
derived from materiality,\ndigital construction protocols,
robotic routines, and\nbottom-up design logics.
