And then in the second\nstep, the concrete material
is deposited on the\nreusable gravel form work.
So this is the first panel\nthat Chris 3D printed
with two layers of concrete.
And so with this\nmethod, one can rapidly
print highly mass customized\nand optimized grid
of thin shell structures.
Printing this with a horizontal\nlayer deposition method
